data.text:
We welcome current Grade 5 (2024) parents and students to attend this tour of Viewbank College.

On the day of your tour, please report to the Performing Arts Centre (there will be signs) at 9.10am for a 9.15am start. The tour will go for approximately 60 minutes followed by a short information session in the Performing Arts Centre.

If you book a tour and circumstances change and you cannot attend, please contact the College to cancel.

Please note these tours are only for parents and students currently in Grade 5.

To meet demands bookings are limited to 3 attendees per family - including your child.

Date: Thursday 5th September, 2024

Venue: Viewbank College Performing Arts Centre, Warren Road, Viewbank, Victoria, 3084

Contact: Deanne, EA to Principal, telephone: 8458 2811, email: viewbank.co@education.vic.gov.au

Please note that parking is on the street only - please allow extra time for parking.
